            <description><![CDATA[【发物影响伤口愈合？发物：这锅我不背<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[二哈]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_erha-139d0e07bd.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】手术后不能吃“发物”？恕我直言这么多年，你可能根本没听懂医嘱在说啥……实际上，伤口愈合需要补充足够的营养，而富含蛋白质和脂肪的“发物”反倒是患者应当重点摄入的对象。至于刺激性发物如辣椒等，只要胃肠功能允许且没有禁忌，并不排斥适量摄入👇🏻（科普中国）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4570377112715289" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">健康界的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/9e0564d7ly1gkm5ooou03j20zk0k0ta3.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/M9I7sa6slx07HWeEeAn601041200PyOB0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;trans_finger=1f0da16358befad33323e3a1b7f95fc9&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1689560542&amp;ssig=Lz7BKeaYEM&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/K4ZPsrN5lx07HWeEaYuQ01041200qnXM0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;trans_finger=62b30a3f061b162e421008955c73f536&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1689560542&amp;ssig=OqvmgzUinz&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/JY0gRzrZlx07HWeE1fHq01041200hpxX0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;trans_finger=40a32e8439c5409a63ccf853562a60ef&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1689560542&amp;ssig=PUcqvZjQZd&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4570377112715289&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
