            <description><![CDATA[【除了致癌风险，代糖也要少喝🙅】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E9%98%BF%E6%96%AF%E5%B7%B4%E7%94%9C%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%91%84%E5%85%A5%E9%87%8F%23&amp;extparam=%23%E9%98%BF%E6%96%AF%E5%B7%B4%E7%94%9C%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%91%84%E5%85%A5%E9%87%8F%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#阿斯巴甜安全摄入量#</span></a>虽然致癌风险等级不算高，代糖也不等于无糖，同样需要注意。经常饮用代糖饮料，可能会影响体内激素分泌，反而造成体重增加，血糖升高，或是心血管患病风险增加👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a> （出品：科普中国-<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%88%9B%E4%BD%9C%E5%9F%B9%E8%82%B2%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%88%9B%E4%BD%9C%E5%9F%B9%E8%82%B2%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#创作培育计划#</span></a> ） <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4913242804518940" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">科普中国的微博视频</span></a> <br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/orj480/005ztyuLly1hfw9ustsrqj61490mndo702.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/KFeZX5eilx086hkjRqVi01041200vtJ20E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1689560542&amp;ssig=lP9bDQ5PHB&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/Uy6LsrNFlx086hkjjCfC01041200giL50E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1689560542&amp;ssig=s%2BgQKRThK0&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/kwjXxRYxlx086hkjhGQo01041200aww90E0